{"tid":749162,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"DONE DEAL!! 艾利臣正式轉投利物浦!!","createTime":"2018-07-19T21:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T01:22:59.000Z","uid":112702,"like":249,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"46f875be0bba46ad8de275dc7e0140c7b1dab2ba","tid":749162,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T21:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/051134_30646d17a7cb12476ccd49f34e1bd6f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F051134_30646d17a7cb12476ccd49f34e1bd6f2.png&h=57bd02b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLiverpool FC have completed the signing of goalkeeper Alisson Becker from AS Roma.<br />\n<br />\nThe 25-year-old signed a long-term contract with the Reds after undergoing a medical and completing the formalities of his switch at Melwood today.<br />\n<br />\nUpon putting pen to paper, the Brazil international told <a href=\"http://Liverpoolfc.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FLiverpoolfc.com&d=a5nv5%2FlCvFTWsFtK5xrHXjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b27aea08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Liverpoolfc.com</a>: &quot;I'm really happy, it's a dream come true to wear such a prestigious shirt for a club of this size that is used to always winning.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;In terms of my life and my career, it's a huge step for me being part of this club and this family.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;You can be certain that I'll give my all.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nAlisson, who began his career with Internacional in his homeland, was Brazil's No.1 at the World Cup in Russia this summer.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.liverpoolfc.com/news/first-team/307801-liverpool-confirm-alisson-deal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.liverpoolfc.com%2Fnews%2Ffirst-team%2F307801-liverpool-confirm-alisson-deal&d=a5nv5%2FlCvFTWsFtK5xrHXjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=4a01e0a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.liverpoolfc.com/news/first-team/307801-liverpool-confirm-alisson-deal</a><br />\n<br />\n正評=值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評=不值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc94428f781f873b85d2cff742a1c46d7425c8f5","tid":749162,"uid":28052,"like":103,"dislike":0,"score":103,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T21:14:21.000Z","msg":"佢去到都派膠就真係利個龍門教練有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf3e6e4cb550887e122413b9d5ecb2d56302143","tid":749162,"uid":112702,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T21:14:58.000Z","msg":"Liverpool will pay &pound;56m guaranteed (&pound;53.8m to Roma and &pound;2.2m to Internacional) plus &pound;9m in add ons, dependant on CL qualification, CL, PL and EL wins.<br />\nLiverpool feared the fee would be &pound;90m in May and &pound;75m in June. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9d88e5535a9807a2cfdc4a0969c2c54fcc978e","tid":749162,"uid":2545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T21:16:56.000Z","msg":"真係all in定我利冠軍都得了"},{"pid":"b22ca761c507585452475bc736c1bb1b1d61b8f1","tid":749162,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T21:19:32.000Z","msg":"Alisson conceded fewer goals (28) than any other goalkeeper to play 25+ Serie A games in 2017/18, keeping 17 clean sheets in 37 matches.<br />\n<br />\nAlisson made 66 saves from shots inside the penalty area in Serie A in 2017/18; more than any other goalkeeper for a top-half side.<br />\n<br />\nAlisson made 46 saves in the 2017/18 Champions League; at least 14 more than any other goalkeeper in the competition.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f01ea43e88e0630e28